,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T00:36:42.000Z","msg":"李克強同雜帝唱反調，離死亡不遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T23:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce6450a4f1420c4ed2a56da319cde69dc3852d7","tid":828662,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T01:01:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對聽眾來說，李克強這次講話最受歡迎的部分是他承諾向中國陷入困境的民營企業釋放資金。</blockquote><br />\n雖然有大大個馬雲做版俾人睇支共點樣圈養套殺, 但支那人見到有水應該已經唔記得, 或者以為自己會係好彩果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}